(Handling Errors) test-case

(When a test checks for an error, the test) should
  (pass if the error is thrown)
  { 1 0 div pop }               % supposed to throw an error
  { pop pop }                   % clean up the unused operands of div
  assert-error

  (fail if the error is not thrown)
  { 1 1 div pop }
  { pop pop }
  assert-error

  (continue with the next test)
  true assert-true

test-summary
